⊢(HTTP_Server) http_server(𝚖,𝚙,𝙷,𝚎):  cors = { access-control-allow-origin=␛* }
  ⊢POST(x): ¿(𝔍󰄟􀍝□)(x)􀯑d􈇇: ↪‹Invalid JSON!›𝖡
